title: I am unable to search for a ranked game
body:
(After patch 6.21)
When i go to que for ranked it comes up with please wait, the screen is black and i can't chose a lane, and after a few seconds (around like 10 or so) it just exits back to the home page and the play button comes back up (time posting is 6:45 am Queensland time)

replies.body:
Thanks for letting us know folks, we're checking it out now.  Will let you know when we know more :)

Cheers
